{"tid":2089400,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"我對我的中國非常失望","createTime":"2020-07-01T15:48:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-02T12:42:54.000Z","uid":45910,"like":94,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"4a381260fef9e077b489fe0be81c081e05eda974","tid":2089400,"uid":45910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T15:48:23.000Z","msg":"本人堅決擁護國安法，但是<br />\n<br />\n中國是世界強國，為甚麼維護國家安全的經費要由小漁村支付，國家付不起嗎？<br />\n<br />\n美國、英國接連煽動香港人對中國的仇恨，國安能快一點去拘捕他們歸案嗎？<br />\n<br />\n今天是中國堂堂正正取回香港的紀念日，怎麼今天國家的安全就受了10次威脅？我們國家是這麼脆弱嗎？<br />\n<br />\n最後，國家的法律我們說了就是，怎麼要有第64條把我們的用字翻譯成小漁村的方言？是預計我們都不能搜索到這條嗎？<br />\n<br />\n我真的很愛中國，求解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"352485a40baaada7580a3b8955e98ef9fdc74884","tid":2089400,"uid":45936,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T15:49:49.000Z","msg":"點解未封facebook IG 等等充滿反華勢力言論既平台？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c4627295879113449cc4757b96ae8452a943595","tid":2089400,"uid":45910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T15:55:34.000Z","msg":"中國可以爭氣一點嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc5c52bcc361d1d552180871e92d16fa7cfa4b88","tid":2089400,"uid":266503,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T15:56:40.000Z","msg":"要攻打美國🇺🇸一統地球"},{"pid":"8fc1ce68af82781a00c30e294d4f718a45fc7746","tid":2089400,"uid":45910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T16:19:17.000Z","msg":"說好的 &quot;厲害了我的國&quot; 呢？"},{"pid":"f2cc9c800fb2da4e513cda96c5e92ec27411686d","tid":2089400,"uid":45910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T17:31:52.000Z","msg":"有人也失望嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cb5f4a41f266928be5fadbeb5584a862a8169f4","tid":2089400,"uid":55913,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T20:15:04.000Z","msg":"藍絲手足<img src=\"/assets